<li><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1133582631"/><cite id="CITEREFXuZaelkeVeldersRamanathan2013" class="citation journal cs1">Xu, Y.; Zaelke, D.; Velders, G. J. M.; Ramanathan, V. (2013). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://acp.copernicus.org/articles/13/6083/2013/acp-13-6083-2013.html">"The role of HFCS in mitigating 21st century climate change"</a>. <i>Atmospheric Chemistry and Physics</i>. <b>13</b> (12): 6083–6089. <a href="/wiki/Bibcode_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Bibcode (identifier)">Bibcode</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2013ACP....13.6083X">2013ACP....13.6083X</a>. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<span class="cs1-lock-free" title="Freely accessible"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.5194%2Facp-13-6083-2013">10.5194/acp-13-6083-2013</a></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Atmospheric+Chemistry+and+Physics&amp;rft.atitle=The+role+of+HFCS+in+mitigating+21st+century+climate+change&amp;rft.volume=13&amp;rft.issue=12&amp;rft.pages=6083-6089&amp;rft.date=2013&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.5194%2Facp-13-6083-2013&amp;rft_id=info%3Abibcode%2F2013ACP....13.6083X&amp;rft.aulast=Xu&amp;rft.aufirst=Y.&amp;rft.au=Zaelke%2C+D.&amp;rft.au=Velders%2C+G.+J.+M.&amp;rft.au=Ramanathan%2C+V.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Facp.copernicus.org%2Farticles%2F13%2F6083%2F2013%2Facp-13-6083-2013.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AOzone+layer" class="Z3988"></span></li>
